{
  "stem": "3331.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in June, in June, the end of June, came the order-- and this was the worst order-- is that the whole town will be taken to Rzeszow, to the larger town.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave us three days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Right away, peasant wagons came, and they loaded the Jews-- the things--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews could take everything what they want.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything, they can take.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a very small German trick, because they wanted to have every Jewish belongings in one place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why should they have, here, the peasants should steal it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everything was taken to this large ghetto, which-- Did you family take everything, or did they leave anything?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we took we took practically everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing we left is furniture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Furniture [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everything-- we had a lot of burlap sacks, sacks from our business, so we load.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got three wagons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Usually you got one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because each sister got a wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We loaded it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I decided-- my family went the first day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my brother had there somebody in the German police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a commandant in the German police who was not in the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a plain policeman, and he used to do business with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German policeman used to go to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to bring saccharine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And saccharine was a very important item, because we didn't have sugar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he used to bring the saccharine, and he used to buy it from me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He used to sell it and make profit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this German policeman-- he was a meister-- came to my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said-- he said he advises him to go with the first day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the first day, the police is in charge.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
